25:34','2026-04-08 19:46:14',0,'18888888888','example@domain.com'),(400437446547906560,'drc9941@outlook.com','a18e78233df17622f4f90938936ac95c','MOJIE','https://rich-tams.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/LOGO.jpg','这个用户很懒，什么都没写。','user','enterprise','互联网/IT','2026-04-11 12:56:27','2026-04-11 12:56:27','2026-04-11 12:56:27',0,NULL,'drc9941@outlook.com');
